title: ASAB Pet Food Storage Container Large 30L/15kg Plastic Food Storage Container With Integrated Food Scoop and Flip Top Locking System Perfect for Dog Treats Dog Food and Kitten Food (Green, Large)
features: PET FOOD CONTAINER - This Pet Food Container is ideal for keeping dry pet food fresh, including dog and cat biscuits, rabbit food, birdseed, and pond fish pellets. Inside this animal feed bin, large amounts of pet food are protected from moisture, and always clean and tidy.

HIGH-QUALITY MATERIAL - The dog food container is made up of BPA-free plastic material, making this storage box sturdy enough to withstand the weight of the stored food without deforming. Perfect for keeping and storing large quantities of dried pet food and bird seed.

SCOOP INCLUDED - This pet food container features a top-locking system with an integrated spoon holder, making it convenient and keeping the food fresh. You can easily manage food portions with the special scooper, which ensures effortless restoration of food from the container.

TILTING LID - The tilting lid of the plastic storage bin is designed to have food immediately available at hand, and the size of the pet food container enables compact and extended storage of feed. This bin is perfect for large dog food as it allows storage of up to 15 kilograms of feed

DIMENSION - The size of the pet food bin is 54cm H x 42cm w, perfect for getting rid of feed bags and betting on a single container that ensures a space-free room in any house. The closure of the food box allows you to keep your animal feed or food in good condition and prevents animals from opening it up.
description: Product Description ASAB Pet Food Storage Box Large 30L/15kg Plastic Food Storage Container With Integrated Food Scoop and Flip Top DOG FOOD BIN This 30L/15kg container is made up of high-quality plastic, ensuring longevity and flexibility. Ideal for keeping your pet's food fresh and secure, it features a flip-top locking system that prevents spills and keeps out moisture and pests. The sleek design complements any home decor, making it a practical and stylish addition to your pet care needs. INTEGRATED FOOD SCOOP The dog food storage comes with a built-in food scoop. This handy tool is perfectly designed to measure the right amount of food, ensuring a consistent diet for your pet. The scoop can attached conveniently inside the lid, which is always accessible and helps to avoid irregularity. VERSATILE STORAGE SOLUTION Dog food storage container aren't just for dogs and cats. Its versatile design makes it an excellent choice for storing birdseed, rabbit pellets, or any other type of dry feed. With a large 30L/15kg capacity, you can store enough supplies, reducing the frequency of refills. EASY TO USE & MAINTAIN Our dog food bin is designed with your convenience in mind. The locking system ensures the food is stored securely, while the container's smooth surfaces make it easy to clean and maintain. Dishwasher-safe and easy to wipe down, this storage box is the perfect solution for maintaining a hygienic feeding area for your beloved pets.
